content.raw:
Carlos, I’ve been working on testing this using the steps above and your tutorial [here](#!/osrf/vrx/wiki/tutorials/acoustic_pingers). In the tutorial, when I run:

```
rostopic echo /wamv/sensors/pingers/pinger/range_bearing
```

I get:

```
ERROR: Cannot load message class for [usv_msgs/RangeBearing]. Are your messages built?
```

Am I missing a step? I’m on the acoustic\_pinger\_plugin branch--maybe the tutorial is meant to run in the default branch?
